Summary:        PCM Up-mix Plug-In for ALSA Library
License:        LGPL-2.1-or-later
Group:          System/Libraries

%description upmix
This package contains a PCM filter plugin that performs multi-channel
upmixing for ALSA library.

%package vdownmix
